{"tid":1807191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"義士唔係Condom，請所有人關注義士！入嚟教你點關注！","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T14:49:50.000Z","uid":145801,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"688ac8f7deddc197df38a2259fec1ca4b38f4471","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"黑警濫捕成風，宜家前線勇武又好、後排和理非都好。基本上所有人都有機會被捕，掟火魔又拉、街坊鬧狗又拉。但係冇一個義士係Condom，全部都係手足。見到今日遊行又拉400個手足，就好嬲好嬲，除咗嬲，大家仲有咩可以做呢？希望大家可以關注下所有義士。關注義士有幾個方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">方法 1. 鍵盤戰士 Follow Telegram 、Instagram 同埋 Facebook</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Telegram</span>有幾個Channel，麻煩全部都Follow<br />\n主Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=d04549a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n義士上庭文字直播Channel:<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=527b5d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a><br />\nGoogle Doc 義士上庭時間表:<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2psqNvm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2psqNvm&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=aeb66318\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2psqNvm</a><br />\n資訊台:<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=16d40063\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info</a><br />\n幫義士搜證搵片台:<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_evidence&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=bf096333\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_evidence</a><br />\n為義士送暖寫信台:<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_mailbox&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=ff654144\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Instagram</span> @youarenotalonehk<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/youarenotalonehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=07e77914\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/youarenotalonehk/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook</span> 最前線 Facebook Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%9C%80%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A-104108750972435/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A-104108750972435%2F&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=af241a2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%9C%80%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A-104108750972435/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">方法 2.親身做啲野</span></span><br />\n包括：拍片錄底手足被捕片段、留意新聞live聽下被捕手足嘅全名、留意下拉咗手足嘅狗車去邊間狗屋、去法院旁聽、做法庭文字直播員、喺公海搵下手足清白嘅片、寫信為手足送暖 Etc etc。<br />\n(手足被人無理還柙，出庭時見到旁聽席無人，一定會好傷心，大家得閒就一定要去旁聽。)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">方法 3.捐款</span></span><br />\n兩大義士基金：星火同盟 &amp; 612人道支援基金 <br />\n自行決定捐邊個，如其捐人血饅頭，捐啲真係幫到義士嘅組織。<br />\n<br />\n義士唔係Condom，希望大家多啲關注義士嘅動向，每一份支持都好重要。<br />\n亦都多謝每一位為義士付出嘅人，特別係被捕關注組一眾Admin、所有義務律師、所有接聽法律求助電話嘅接線生、所有拍低手足無罪嘅記者、所有捐過錢嘅善長人翁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家喺下面同佢地講聲多謝、同義士講聲多謝，順便推下Post等多啲人關注義士。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求！缺一不可！<br />\n釋放所有被捕義士！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTn705J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTn705J.jpg&h=4b1f74c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dcebcef0d0c7efdc998443147b8147766907330","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:31:43.000Z","msg":"關注義士！"},{"pid":"b2b6b13932522611aece172d805f245795e74f08","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"釋放義士！"},{"pid":"421c76f836b95252a00afb8100ef0a5587c9e68b","tid":1807191,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ebbdd99bd4a92af40908b49c3a35c4f1b0e336b","tid":1807191,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e569ec68988c54e58b51bc29bb1d419332e7233","tid":1807191,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:32:46.000Z","msg":"還我公義"},{"pid":"1ad9b733b717fa94b6603a9640a8de0086829036","tid":1807191,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1438bd60e4b78a3ecaf7790bc13eb5fc4148522c","tid":1807191,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01fc76cd5273e2f44482d8189800a8e7ae91470a","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"沒有暴徒！"},{"pid":"740817661d0e487d329174f7894c670cd722ec59","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:33:44.000Z","msg":"只有暴政！"},{"pid":"7132ed87d6400ec8559d2b3432c9b2f0b8e127b9","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"釋放義士！還我公義！"},{"pid":"6e696e696e6711f2aaa3c13969fccd149780d50b","tid":1807191,"uid":145801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"幫下手關注下